Player Controls
---------------
Use the mouse to rotate ship. Move forward and back with thw W and S keys.

Known Bugs
---------------
- Particle Spawners seem to stop emitting after spawning a certain number of particles
- Mouse look generates some camera shake, the algorithim to calculate rotations is poorly designed
- Enemy Follow is broken

